{"word":"H5133 - נֹוצָה - nôwtsâh - no-tsaw' - Feather","slug":"H5133","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נֹוצָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nôwtsâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>no-tsaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Feather"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05E6;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E0;&#x05D5;&#x05E6;&#x05D4; - no&#x0302;tsa&#x0302;h  no&#x0302;tsa&#x0302;h</b> - <i>no-tsaw', no-tsaw'</i><p/>Feminine active participle of <a href=\"#/H5327\">H5327</a> in the sense of <i>flying</i>; a <i>pinion</i> (or wing feather); often (collectively) <i>plumage: - </i>feather (-s), ostrich."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5132\">H5132</a>"}]}